column6:
If you want a Page that helps you learn more about vaping with no lies and no bullsh*t, you've come to the right Page.

We got live commentaries, product review and more in this Page.

If you happen to drop by, like and follow my Page.
column31: “The vaping industry is being treated unfairly. We are not the enemy here. Combustible cigarettes that bring 88,000 deaths per year are our common enemy. Why is vaping treated worse than smoking?” Sabi pa ng president ng Philippine E-Cigarette Industry Association na si Joey Dulay, mas harsh pa ang regulations sa alternative nicotine-delivery systems kaysa sa traditional cigarettes. Maling-mali talaga eh. Diba mga bros? #VaperAko #advocacy #KaiDefiantVaping
